body_html:
I tried all recipes above but stuck having build error:

Making clean in . /bin/sh: /Volumes/Macintosh: No such file or directory make: *** [clean-recursive] Error 1

So, I did fix that by changing path to my Xcode not to have delimiters like spaces:

/Volumes/Macintosh HD/Xcode 8.2.app -> /Volumes/Macintosh-HD/Xcode.app

and now I can succesfully build:

tensorflow/contrib/makefile/compile_ios_protobuf.sh

body:
I tried all recipes above but stuck having build error:

`Making clean in .
/bin/sh: /Volumes/Macintosh: No such file or directory
make: *** [clean-recursive] Error 1
`

So, I did fix that by changing path to my Xcode not to have delimiters like spaces:

`/Volumes/Macintosh HD/Xcode 8.2.app -> /Volumes/Macintosh-HD/Xcode.app `

and now I can succesfully build:

`tensorflow/contrib/makefile/compile_ios_protobuf.sh `
